        <article class="suds-home-ladder-card">
          <div class="suds-home-ladder-card__image">
            <img src="{{ stock_elite_image }}" loading="lazy" alt="Machine polishing black paint during Elite Detail mobile detailing">
          </div>
          <div class="suds-home-ladder-card__body">
            <p>Heavy reset</p>
            <h3>Elite Detail</h3>
            {%- if elite_product != blank -%}<strong>Starting at {{ elite_product.price | money_without_trailing_zeros }}</strong>{%- endif -%}
            <span>For pet vehicles, family SUVs, resale prep, rougher paint feel, and vehicles needing more time.</span>
            <ul>
              <li>Deep interior cleaning and stain attention</li>
              <li>Clay, wax, wheels, tires, finish work</li>
              <li>Approx. 5-8 hours depending on condition</li>
