            <p>Add real Suds photos to this homepage section in Shopify. Put the Ferrari photo in the first gallery block for the strongest proof image.</p>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </section>
  {%- endif -%}

  <section class="suds-home-final">
    <div class="suds-home-shell">
      <p class="suds-home-final__eyebrow">Owner-operator walk-through</p>
      <h2>If You're Not Happy, Sam Looks at It With You. Period.</h2>
      <p>Every detail ends with a walk-through. If something reasonable was missed, Suds addresses it on the spot when possible before the appointment is wrapped.</p>
      <div class="suds-home-actions suds-home-actions--center">
        <a class="suds-home-button suds-home-button--gold" href="{{ booking_url }}">Book My Mobile Detail &rarr;</a>
        <a class="suds-home-button suds-home-button--black" href="{{ quote_url }}">Request a Quote</a>
      </div>
      <a class="suds-home-final__text" href="sms:+14253618838">Or text (425) 361-8838 with photos</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <nav class="suds-home-mobile-bar" aria-label="Quick mobile booking actions">
    <a href="tel:+14253618838">Call</a>
    <a href="{{ booking_url }}">Book</a>
  </nav>
</main>

